    prov:wasAssociatedWith agent:human-author , agent:claude-opus-4-7 , agent:provenance-curator ;
    rdfs:comment "Researcher direction: 'validate provenance i think there are some unconnected entites'. Ran a 9-query audit (parentless claims, ghost sources, orphan activities, orphan sections, unused figures, contributions without prov:influenced, unused agents, unused transcripts, untyped IRIs). Fixes applied: (a) verif:lit-retrieved + verif:lit-read declared with a fair2r:VerificationState type (the other rungs were already declared; these two had been overlooked); (b) ent:section-implementation typed as a fair2r:Section so the prov:wasDerivedFrom edge from ent:section-appendix-implementation points at a typed entity; (c) act:invalidate-discussion-section connected to act:rev-reconcile-and-illustrate via prov:wasInformedBy with an rdfs:comment naming the now-removed Discussion section; (d) four agent IRIs (orchestrator, source-analyzer, condenser, presentation) connected via prov:wasAssociatedWith to activities that used them in practice; (e) ent:transcript-2026-05-07 bound to its parent activity via prov:used. Documented but unfixed: 28 ghost sources (the verification scoping doc names this number; ghost-cite tolerance is intentional) and 13 unused observations (hypothesis-stage by design, will gain prov:influenced when they graduate)."@en .

hc:provenance-graph-hygiene-pass  a fair2r:HumanContribution ;
    rdfs:label "Researcher direction: validate provenance, fix unconnected entities"@en ;
    fair2r:contributedBy agent:human-author ;
    fair2r:contributionType "corrective-intervention" ;
    fair2r:contributionLeverage "medium" ;
    rdfs:comment "Audit + fix pass. The audit's 9 queries are now checkable invariants: parentless claims (was 0, still 0); ghost sources (28, documented); orphan activities (was 1, now 0); orphan sections (0); unused figures (8, all with prov:wasGeneratedBy --- query was over-strict); contributions without prov:influenced (13, all hypothesis-stage observations); unused agents (was 4, now 0); unused transcripts (was 1, now 0); untyped IRIs (was 2, now 0)."@en ;
    dcterms:created "2026-05-08"^^xsd:date ;
    prov:influenced act:provenance-graph-hygiene-pass .

# Hygiene-pass follow-up: declare ent:section-discussion (the section
# the orphan activity invalidated) and connect it explicitly so the
